        <h2>Hi there!</h2> 
        <h2>I'm Maya De Marco.</h2>
        <p>
          I am a Montreal based graphic and web designer. I am currently a third year student at Vanier College enrolled
          in Micromedia who is always looking to learn, collaborate, and share with passionate individuals just like me.
          I aspire to help those I work with bring the love for their ideas to life.
        </p>
        <p>
          I mostly enjoy working with branding, layout, illustration, and typography, however, I am capable of adapting
          to your needs to make your most creative and innovative ideas blossom. My design style is mostly clean,
          effective, organized, and serious but I will never pass up the opportunity to add a pop of colour and
          playfulness to my work. I strongly believe that conceptualization, intention, and meaning are at the heart of
          good design.
        </p>
